{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>给出一个有向图G=(V, E)，和一个源点v0∈V，请写一个程序输出v0和图G中其它顶点的最短路径。只要所有的有向环权值和都是正的，我们就允许图的边有负值。顶点的标号从1到n（n为图G的顶点数）。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"最短路径 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>共包含n-1行，按照顶点编号从小到大的顺序，每行输出源点v0到一个顶点的最短距离。每行的具体格式参照样例。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第1行：一个正数n（2≤n≤80），表示图G的顶点总数。<p><p>第2行：一个整数，表示源点v0（v0∈V，v0可以是图G中任意一个顶点）。<p><p>第3至第n+2行，用一个邻接矩阵W给出了这个图。<p>","examples":"<input>5\n1\n0 2 - - 10\n- 0 3 - 7\n- - 0 4 -\n- - - 0 5\n- - 6 - 0\n</input><output>(1 -> 2) = 2\n(1 -> 3) = 5\n(1 -> 4) = 9\n(1 -> 5) = 9\n\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"样例所对应的图如下:\n![](pic/1378.gif)\n","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1378","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}